Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.01,0:00:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,So the lizard won't die even if you chop his head off?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.29,0:00:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.74,0:00:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you remember the face of the man inside his mouth clearly?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.71,0:00:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.11,0:00:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The man and the lizard both had cross-marks on their eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.31,0:00:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Cross-marks, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.94,0:00:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And the woman who was with him was a sorcerer?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.00,0:00:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, her name is Nikaido.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.36,0:00:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll look into her at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.21,0:00:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I know a sorcerer who's called "Turkey".
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.40,0:00:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,His dolls should prove useful when it comes to the lizard-man.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.69,0:02:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Turkey. I'm a sorcerer who makes living dolls.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.77,0:02:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Living dolls?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.34,0:02:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't believe me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.26,0:02:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Should I make one to demonstrate?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.43,0:02:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Please put smoke into this bottle while thinking about someone you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.18,0:02:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,She should be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.25,0:02:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, please wait a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.88,0:02:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Turkey's dolls...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.92,0:02:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Are alive and imitate the habits and behavior of the original.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.00,0:02:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And the interesting thing about these dolls is...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.40,0:02:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That they tend to go where the original is.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.42,0:02:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.75,0:02:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,If you make a doll of the man inside his mouth and follow it...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.65,0:02:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You might be able to figure out the lizard-man's identity.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.43,0:03:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I have finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.69,0:03:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, bon app√©tit!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.24,0:03:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,How is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.50,0:03:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't she just like your partner, from head to toe?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.08,0:03:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. As expected of you, Turkey, it's exactly like Noi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.87,0:03:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, Shin?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.34,0:03:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,How should I know something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.24,0:03:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Senpai! Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.11,0:03:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Shin-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.26,0:03:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,- Hurry up and get rid of it! Get rid of it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.04,0:03:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to intrude... Ah, senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.94,0:03:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry I'm late!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.14,0:03:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... My mask? Did you bring it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.03,0:03:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.97,0:03:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? Something smells really good!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.59,0:03:49.00,Title,,0,0,0,,{\c&H0049DB&\pos(960,670)}Roast Duck\N{\c&HF13CB9&}With a Sorcerer
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.01,0:03:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then, I shall now explain how I make the dolls.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.32,0:03:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Here are the ingredients.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.08,0:03:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Finely chop some onions and celery and mix them up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.25,0:03:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Add cognac, port wine, salt and pepper and mix well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.41,0:04:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Once you've beaten and flattened the duck, roll it and tie it up using kite string and put it in the oven.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.89,0:04:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Baste it with Shin's smoke and veal stock every ten minutes...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.55,0:04:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And roast slowly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.29,0:04:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So good...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.66,0:04:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's done!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.16,0:04:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,How is it? Remind you of anyone, En?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.90,0:04:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope, nobody.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.74,0:04:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, let's keep an eye on what the doll does and find out what kind of a person he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.87,0:04:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,He must be the key to solving the mystery of this lizard-bastard.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.08,0:04:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,We're kinda like detectives! This is fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.32,0:04:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Getting a job like this is nice every once in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.38,0:04:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? He's going into that store.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.51,0:04:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he going to change into something he's more used to?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.90,0:04:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What a cheap store again... Is he broke?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.99,0:05:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Clerk, do you know that man?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.40,0:05:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope, I only started here last week.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.06,0:05:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Blaka Smoko, Enter The Hole, She Is A Devil...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.90,0:05:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,- Hey, Ebisu...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.17,0:05:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You smell like a zombie, get some clothes from here and change.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.89,0:05:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Suits you well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.29,0:05:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Lookin' cool?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.49,0:05:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss customer, that's just underwear...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.61,0:05:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,This time it's a restaurant?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.16,0:05:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-This place is really expensive, senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.79,0:05:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Waiter, do you know this guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.42,0:05:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,He has supposedly been a customer here before...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.68,0:05:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I do not know him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.81,0:05:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I have been working at this restaurant for thirty years, but I never...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.57,0:05:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll have the strawberry terrine in jelly, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.01,0:05:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Next up is a train, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.86,0:05:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But still, this guy... His clothes are cheap, but he eats at members-only restaurants...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.86,0:05:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Just what kind of a person is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.12,0:05:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,If I had to say...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.33,0:05:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't need to hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.39,0:06:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.10,0:06:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The people who can't use any decent magic...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.23,0:06:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Gather here and find some solace by forming groups.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.17,0:06:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,People who are naturally not able to produce much smoke...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.40,0:06:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Or whose magic just plain sucks...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.72,0:06:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I might not be too far off from that myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.04,0:06:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if this is his apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.97,0:06:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The original isn't here...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.87,0:06:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go and ask the landlord.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.62,0:06:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.88,0:06:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys look for any clues.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.89,0:06:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.35,0:06:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Haven't seen the guy from room 8 for about a year now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.70,0:06:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,A year? What's his name?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.25,0:06:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't know his name or his face.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.65,0:07:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a common thing to keep things private in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.84,0:07:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll find something and be useful too!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.23,0:07:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? Fujita!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.26,0:07:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? Did you find something?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.05,0:07:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Are you alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.70,0:07:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,E-Ebisu found a box and...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.41,0:07:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,The doll suddenly reacted...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.22,0:07:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.89,0:07:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, you duck meat doll. Hand the box over.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.28,0:07:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,If you try to resist me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.57,0:07:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll break you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.52,0:07:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,A safe...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.38,0:07:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.63,0:08:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoops!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.27,0:08:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You little...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.75,0:08:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Never thought a duck steak would get a hit on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.60,0:08:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Senpai! These two are okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.89,0:08:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The doll broke, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.49,0:08:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,There should be some clues about the original in this safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.89,0:08:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Noi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.77,0:08:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.67,0:08:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! H-He's...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.35,0:08:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? Oh my!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.03,0:08:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,So the man inside the mouth was already dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.43,0:08:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,In the end we didn't learn anything, damnit!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.70,0:08:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.61,0:09:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep this head in your bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.96,0:09:13.18,Title 2,,0,0,0,,{\c&H000000&\3c&H4F2ABA&\pos(372,688)\frz39.28}Please Attend\NThe Dance In\NFormal Attire
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.77,0:09:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Before we enter the venue, put these on.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.64,0:09:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Nose plugs?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.85,0:09:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Just what kind of a party is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.04,0:09:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll understand when you get in.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.81,0:09:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,These are... corpses?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.33,0:09:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Smells so bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.50,0:09:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is why we plugged our noses...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.16,0:09:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And I was really looking forward to the free food.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.08,0:09:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying? The food's right there. Eat as much as you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.12,0:09:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,This party is held once a year.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.98,0:09:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,All participants bring their own corpse to the gathering.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.04,0:09:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Really now... A party for corpse lovers?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.40,0:09:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this weird background noise? It's coming from that dark ceiling...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.58,0:10:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Flies.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.81,0:10:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,After this, the sorcerer who can give life will come.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.76,0:10:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,She will revive these corpses.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.69,0:10:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The boxes attached to the corpses are presents for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.07,0:10:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's her...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.42,0:10:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,She should be able to revive that decapitated head. Right, senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.40,0:10:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.36,0:10:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? Isn't that Ebisu?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.29,0:10:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,She's with... En?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.16,0:10:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you been to this party before, Ebisu?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.60,0:10:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.73,0:10:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Ebisu's name was on a list of past guests.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.58,0:10:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,She could be useful somehow...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.18,0:10:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.81,0:10:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, the guests of honor are here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.87,0:10:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Those lame-ass guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.76,0:10:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's starting.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.77,0:10:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorcerers have a small tumor in their heads.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.40,0:11:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's shaped like a devil and represents our life to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.62,0:11:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,White smoke...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.97,0:11:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.17,0:11:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,- Little devil!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.08,0:11:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The corpse... Came back to life!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.77,0:11:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.94,0:11:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then, I have a job for you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.15,0:11:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.57,0:11:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,A job?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.18,0:11:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Just what was your true motive for coming here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.94,0:11:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm making her my partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.16,0:11:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Come again?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.96,0:11:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,For several years now...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.57,0:11:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I have been searching for a worthy sorcerer to become my partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.97,0:11:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I see... And now you've finally found one?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.71,0:11:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You really are such a pompous guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.30,0:12:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,To tell you the truth, I've been looking for a sorcerer who can control time, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.77,0:12:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.34,0:12:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it, Ebisu?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.53,0:12:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What? The toilet?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.07,0:12:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Go by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.94,0:12:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Shin. Noi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.22,0:12:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You shall now erase that man.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.66,0:12:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill him and throw the body somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.32,0:12:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.14,0:12:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Little miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.71,0:12:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.67,0:12:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Little miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.67,0:12:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a balloon!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.98,0:12:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Look! C'mere, c'mere!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.82,0:12:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.01,0:12:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, everyone. Please enjoy chatting for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.67,0:12:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go after them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.38,0:12:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Been a while, Ebisu!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.74,0:12:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You really surprised me! You coming here with En...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.97,0:12:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Just what are you up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.54,0:12:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, that's right! I've got some good powder!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.51,0:12:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Been a while, right? Give it a try...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.77,0:12:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Booze!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.34,0:12:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a secret, but the organizers of this party...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.37,0:13:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Are our customers too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.18,0:13:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't control this guy with my magic alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.08,0:13:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Did the man with the cross-eyes bring enough black powder?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.54,0:13:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and take the powder, you still haven't revived even half of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.96,0:13:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha-?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.83,0:13:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,That woman will become En's partner. Give her up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.41,0:13:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What's this? So En was aiming for that too?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.57,0:13:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Damnit!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.25,0:13:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.36,0:14:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a while since we've had an opponent we could show our combo to!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.83,0:14:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Whenever you're ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.45,0:14:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Fools!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.56,0:14:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.55,0:14:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.96,0:14:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.00,0:14:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.30,0:14:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You are... En!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.47,0:14:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.86,0:14:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You will be my partner starting from today.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.14,0:14:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.55,0:14:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Black powder...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.11,0:14:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Even she was using the powder...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.74,0:14:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What a disgrace for a sorcerer...! Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.21,0:14:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.65,0:14:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The black powder the guy used...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.40,0:14:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Is a drug that temporarily boosts your magic power and gets you addicted to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.48,0:14:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh... Why did he use something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.23,0:15:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,When you suck really bad, this stuff is necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.90,0:15:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, En.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.35,0:15:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Did it go well with... What the hell is that animal?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.98,0:15:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the "life-giving sorcerer".
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.80,0:15:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,That woman was hiding this guy under her dress.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.89,0:15:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Whaa... so this is your new partner now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.83,0:15:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, no... That's not really...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.60,0:15:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Senpai! Let's give it a name!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.19,0:15:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Ebisu!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.13,0:15:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Where have you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.84,0:15:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,There's your toilet...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.32,0:15:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And there's your food bowl...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.58,0:15:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You really built one hell of a place.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.71,0:15:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss has a ton of money.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.31,0:15:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I had a devil make the mask.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.70,0:15:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Must be nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.99,0:15:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Fujita's really jealous, no joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.55,0:15:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,En, have you found out anything about Nikaido?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.30,0:15:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I looked her up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.05,0:16:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,She went across to Hole when she was a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.39,0:16:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss scoops up shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.21,0:16:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,However, I couldn't find out what kind of magic she uses.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.57,0:16:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Since she was a kid, there wasn't that much information about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.18,0:16:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That stinks!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.51,0:16:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,So then, it's possible that the one who cast the magic on the lizard-man...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.01,0:16:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Was this Nikaido, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.09,0:16:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Your belly is so fluffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.60,0:16:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,- Yeah. If we use this guy's magic to revive the severed head...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.97,0:16:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. If we use this guy's magic to revive the severed head...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.64,0:16:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,We might find out something about that too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.32,0:16:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And while we're at it, I'll have this guy bring back to life
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.15,0:16:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,This precious mushroom I accidentally let rot.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.11,0:16:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The head seems to be completely secondary to him...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.14,0:16:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss, Ebisu has come up with some names for the animal.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.78,0:16:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I give list. Boss excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.61,0:16:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,They're all names of evil spirits!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.17,0:16:45.13,Handwriting,,0,0,0,,{\c&H000000&\frz27.61\pos(338,344)}Puki
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.17,0:16:45.13,Handwriting,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,590)\c&H000000&\frz32.54}Pug
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.17,0:16:45.13,Handwriting,,0,0,0,,{\c&H000000&\frz34.83\pos(1454,396)}Parka
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.17,0:16:45.13,Handwriting,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1240,328)\frz37.34\c&H000000&}Ashka
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.17,0:16:45.13,Handwriting,,0,0,0,,{\pos(996,904)\c&H000000&\frz27.31}Divas
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.77,0:16:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I appreciate it, but I've already decided on a name.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.91,0:16:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,"Kikurage".
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.36,0:16:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Flutter, flutter...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.88,0:16:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,- Don't these fluttery things remind you of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.23,0:16:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Fluttery and fluffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.34,0:16:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, whatever...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.47,0:17:03.77,Title,,0,0,0,,{\c&HF4F3EF&\pos(960,550)}The years come and go\Nin Hole
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.86,0:17:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's really gotten cold now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.52,0:17:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to drag you along on New Year's Eve.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.08,0:17:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,This "Professor" we're visiting now...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.12,0:17:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of a guy is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.65,0:17:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,A friend of Doc's. Apparently he's the leading expert in sorcerer research.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.79,0:17:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if he's gonna be some grumpy old man...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.20,0:17:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,"Kasukabe"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.80,0:17:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? There's no response at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.12,0:17:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The lock is open.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.35,0:17:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Professor?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.95,0:17:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,We've come to deliver sorcerers' corpses for research!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.08,0:17:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.91,0:17:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It's pitch-black.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.82,0:17:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if the professor has dropped dead somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.41,0:17:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I'd ask him a bunch of questions about sorcerers.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.65,0:17:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hasn't the number of sorcerers really gone down lately?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.24,0:17:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Hole is peaceful, but that's bad news for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.70,0:17:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish I could go to the world of sorcerers!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.93,0:18:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What're you gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.27,0:18:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,If we happen to find a way to their world...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.48,0:18:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You're gonna come with me for sure, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.51,0:18:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this? Don't tell me you're scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.21,0:18:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... Really scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.93,0:18:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It's gonna be fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.72,0:18:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll protect you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.68,0:18:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? Nikaido, that room...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.82,0:18:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorcerer specimens...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.24,0:18:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like the bloodstained lab of a mad doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.97,0:18:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Look! It's the masks of the sorcerers we've killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.81,0:18:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Is someone there?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.86,0:18:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The room next to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.37,0:18:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,T-There ain't a room next to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.11,0:18:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I see... this entire house must have been distorted by magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.44,0:18:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The smoke that's accumulated in the corpses of the sorcerers...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.92,0:18:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Is now filling the mansion as dust.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.77,0:19:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like a maze in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.71,0:19:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no use! The Professor ain't here and I'm starving!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.23,0:19:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna die at this rate!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.13,0:19:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.24,0:19:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the kitchen!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.31,0:19:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurray! Let's eat something!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.47,0:19:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What should I make?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.58,0:19:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Gyoza!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.86,0:19:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.72,0:19:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Happy new year!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.12,0:19:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,New Year's dishes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.71,0:19:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead and eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.61,0:19:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The herring roe is so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.73,0:19:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Nikaido...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.67,0:19:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.89,0:19:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I've always been meaning to say this...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.49,0:19:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for being my friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.93,0:19:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Are you an idiot? What's this all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.97,0:20:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what happens, keep being my friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.69,0:20:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this now? Of course I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.38,0:20:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Phew! So good!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.20,0:20:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Caiman, listen...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.56,0:20:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,There's something I also really need to tell you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.90,0:20:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It's snowing!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.12,0:20:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,So pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.56,0:20:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it okay if I have this omelet roll?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.95,0:20:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.02,0:20:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Tasty!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.33,0:20:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.52,0:20:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Professor Kasukabe!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.66,0:20:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I live in this mansion and do experiments on sorcerers.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.95,0:20:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha-?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.99,0:20:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,The hell you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.89,0:20:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I've heard about you guys from Vaux.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.27,0:20:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The professor was just a child?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.76,0:20:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I was used for practice by a sorcerer and turned into a kid
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.92,0:20:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm actually around sixty years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.32,0:21:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Somehow, I lucked out!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.99,0:21:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you been wandering around this house the whole time?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.75,0:21:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! Who'd get lost in their own house?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.92,0:21:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just doing some serious cleaning.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.92,0:21:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,See? Because I cleaned up, the house became normal again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.16,0:21:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.68,0:21:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.49,0:21:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Caiman...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.49,0:21:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.69,0:21:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to show you something good!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.75,0:21:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the only thing that connects our Hole and their world.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.45,0:21:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I researched it and finally succeeded in reproducing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.07,0:21:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,But I wonder if you're prepared to try it out?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.41,0:21:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a door made out of sorcerer carcasses and bones.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.96,0:21:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Their world lies beyond this.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.72,0:23:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What we learned from the fourth curse:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.56,0:23:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,1. The man inside the mouth is already dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.07,0:23:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,2. En is looking for a partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.24,0:23:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,3. Hole celebrates New Year's Eve.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.88,0:23:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And what you will learn from the fifth curse...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.85,0:23:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That's still a mystery.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.20,0:23:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That is...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.11,0:23:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,DOROHEDORO

